import styled from "styled-components"

const Container = styled.div``
const Wrapper = styled.div``
const Header = styled.div``
const HeaderBgText = styled.div``
const HeaderSmText = styled.div``
function ResetPassword() {
  return (
    <Container className="flex aic jcc" >
      <Wrapper className='flex aic jcc fdc' >
        <Header>
         <HeaderBgText>Reset Your Password</HeaderBgText>
         <HeaderSmText>Fear not.Send an OTP to your Email</HeaderSmText>
        </Header>
      </Wrapper>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default ResetPassword
